<p><strong>Primary Visualizations</strong></p>
<p>Okay, so after much fiddling, I could simply not figure out how to connect the <strong>host_cities</strong> to their countries for my beautiful mapping plans. I just kept creating larger and larger datasets. At one point I think I had about 20 million cases and I do NOT want to crash my computer, so. We will forego the map for now. But someday. Someday I <em>will</em> make a world map of all the gold medals we have won.</p>
<p>Let’s make a lollipop plot instead, of the countries with the top 10 number of gold medals.</p>
